Download for free on itch.io https://hauntedps1.itch.io/demodisc2021?ac=qfCyYFQF-yt With a storm on the horizon, a sled dog musher is hired to transport a strange scientst into the mountains. Lead a team of realistic sled dogs on a tense arctic mission. Brave the hostile yet beautiful barren wastes of the tundra. Follow a mysterious companion into the unknown!
